<h1>Settings</h1>
<p>The settings page surfaces configuration options sourced from the server. The skeleton app exposes the following environment driven settings:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Storage directory and naming format for entries</li>
    <li>Transcription provider (API or local sidecar)</li>
    <li>Summarization provider and model</li>
    <li>Automatic title generation provider</li>
    <li>Authentication via OpenID Connect</li>
</ul>
<p>Implement server APIs to expose and persist configuration as needed.</p>
